Croton persimilis 
<normalizedToken id="D95F6ABAD157A20E2FD226D81A1ABEC4" originalValue="Müll">Muell</normalizedToken>
. Arg. (= C. oblongifolius Roxb.)
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
